@ncw ,

Oh, Docker Hub does not support incremental builds. Now it only has the build for the `linux/arm/v6` platform (https://hub.docker.com/r/rclone/rclone/tags).

You need to pass all target platforms in the `platform` option, like this: `--platform linux/amd64,linux/386,linux/arm64,linux/arm/v7,linux/arm/v6`.
